Comment: Display the default and custom Management Role Assignment without delegating MRA

PSCmdL: $AllMR=Get-ManagementRole | ? { $_.IsRootRole -eq $false -and $_.IsEndUserRole -eq $false };$allmresult=@(); foreach ($MR in $allMR){ $allMRE=Get-ManagementRoleEntry -Identity "$($MR.identity)\*"  | select Role,Name,@{Name='Parameters';Expression={[string]::join(";",($_.Parameters))}},WhenCreated,WhenChanged; foreach ($MRE in  $allMRE){$MREobj = [PSCustomObject]@{ Role = $MRE.Role;RoleType = $mr.RoleType;Name = $MRE.name;Parameters = $MRE.Parameters;WhenCreated = $MRE.WhenCreated;WhenChanged = $MRE.WhenChanged};$allmresult+=$MREobj}};$allmresult
